name: Into the Depths Bellow...
description: Moddest Map 03. A caverns dank depths. A very good map with some twists n' turn n' death! Let the imps be. For those who don't know, "Moddest Mapping" or MM, is a challenge where mappers have to make a map with 4 enemy types max, 40 sectors max, and no SSG. Mappers could pick map slot(s) and make a map.
